# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:39
translate spanish hwb_s10b_3851e766:

    # "As we turn round a curve in the road, the tour group comes into view."
    "Al doblar una curva del camino, el grupo turístico aparece a la vista."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s10b_2c47013b:

    # "Just ahead is a cluster of people, most of them armed with flashlights. It’s hard to know for sure, but I can see at least a dozen different figures."
    "Justo adelante hay un grupo de personas, la mayoría armadas con linternas. Es difícil saber con certeza, pero puedo ver al menos una docena de figuras distintas."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s10b_ef37a630:

    # "The tour guide is shining his light up at a rock face, illuminating some designs on it. Everyone has their backs to us."
    "El guía turístico ilumina con su linterna una pared rocosa, revelando algunos diseños en ella. Todos están de espaldas a nosotros."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s10b_2dac6505:

    # Amber "Try to be as sneaky as possible."
    Amber "Крадись настолько тихо, насколько можешь."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s10b_83a2405b:

    # Amber "We wanna join up without them noticing, like we've been there the whole time."
    Amber "Мы к ним прибьемся так, что они даже не заметят, что нас тут раньше не было."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s10b_e910fbe9:

    # Amber "If anyone notices us show up, they might notice when we leave."
    Amber "Если кто-нибудь заметит, как мы подходим, то могут заметить, когда мы улизнем."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6fe54032:

    # Marina "Why do we have to join up in the first place?"
    Marina "Почему нам нужно присоединиться к ним в первом же месте?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s10b_062beee2:

    # Amber "I don’t know how to get to the ruins we’re looking for. We’ll stay with the group until the tour gets there, and then we’ll sneak off."
    Amber "Я не знаю, как добраться до руин, которые нам нужны. Мы будем с группой, пока гид нас туда не приведет, а затем улизнем."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s10b_8cca6a15:

    # "Marina nods."
    "Marina asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s10b_646fc6fa:

    # Amber "Okay, follow my lead. And remember, be as quiet as you can."
    Amber "Хорошо, иди за мной. И запомни, веди себя настолько тихо, насколько только можешь."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:76
translate spanish hwb_s10b_90f71b29:

    # "We creep forward, slowly. If someone were to turn around and see us, we’d look pretty suspicious. But nobody does. The lecture on petroglyphs gets their full attention."
    "Nos arrastramos hacia adelante, lentamente. Si alguien se girara y nos viera, pareceríamos bastante sospechosas. Pero nadie lo hace. La conferencia sobre los petroglifos acapara toda su atención."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:78
translate spanish hwb_s10b_2ee8852b:

    # "Marina kicks a rock and I tense up, expecting that to break the spell. But we’re close enough now that if it did, it might not matter."
    "Marina patea una piedra y yo me tenso, esperando que eso rompa el hechizo. Pero ya estamos lo suficientemente cerca como para que, si ocurriera, quizás ya no importe."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:84
translate spanish hwb_s10b_7350fe09:

    # "And we reach the back of the tour group without anyone noticing. I give Marina a thumbs-up, which she returns."
    "Y llegamos al final del grupo turístico sin que nadie se dé cuenta. Le hago un pulgar arriba a Marina, y ella me devuelve el gesto."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:86
translate spanish hwb_s10b_dc939aa1:

    # Guide ". . . Anasazi ruins. Some of the Navajo people still call the area home. There’s a living community in the canyon, who…"
    Guide ". . . Руины Анасази. Некоторые из племени Навахо все еще зовут их домом. В каньоне осталось поселение, которое…"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:92
translate spanish hwb_s10b_04ebf8ae:

    # "I’m not too interested hearing about the history of the place, so I turn back to Marina. She’s looking up at the pictures too, though her eyes appear glazed over."
    "No me interesa mucho escuchar la historia del lugar, así que me giro hacia Marina. Ella también está mirando las imágenes, aunque sus ojos parecen vidriosos."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s10b_e5a7265e:

    # "When she catches me staring, she blinks and then smiles. I smile back, though I must look like an idiot just watching her instead of the lecture."
    "Cuando me descubre mirándola, parpadea y luego sonríe. Le devuelvo la sonrisa, aunque debo parecer una idiota solo viéndola a ella en lugar de la conferencia."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s10b_7aca727c:

    # "After a minute, the guide’s speech concludes and we start to walk down the trail. Much to my dismay, before I can say anything to Marina, the woman in front of us turns around."
    "Después de un minuto, el discurso del guía concluye y empezamos a caminar por el sendero. Para mi desgracia, antes de que pueda decirle algo a Marina, la mujer frente a nosotras se da la vuelta."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s10b_29951fc0:

    # Woman "Isn’t that just crazy?"
    Woman "Разве это не сумасшествие?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s10b_1220824c:

    # Amber "Huh?"
    Amber "А?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s10b_055392fb:

    # "It takes a second for me to understand that she’s talking to me. She fits just about every stereotype of ‘redneck’, from the huge hat on her head to the baby strapped to her chest."
    "Tardo un segundo en entender que me está hablando a mí. Encaja en casi todos los estereotipos de \"pueblerina\", desde el enorme sombrero en su cabeza hasta el bebé atado a su pecho."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:127
translate spanish hwb_s10b_a178245e:

    # "She'd probably be attractive, if not for the layers of sunscreen coating her face. Even though it's nearly nighttime. They make her look like a ghost."
    "Probablemente sería atractiva, si no fuera por las capas de protector solar que cubren su rostro. Aunque ya es casi de noche. La hacen parecer un fantasma."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s10b_997bb3d5:

    # Woman "I said, isn’t that just crazy? What he was saying about those Indians and how they used to communicate with each other."
    Woman "Я сказала, не сумасшествие ли это? То, что он рассказывал про тех индейцев и то, как они общались друг с другом."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s10b_247ec091:

    # Amber "Oh, yeah."
    Amber "Ах, да."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s10b_5ea2b6dd:

    # "Even if I had wanted to talk to her, I still have no idea what the guide had said."
    "Incluso si hubiera querido hablar con ella, todavía no tengo idea de lo que dijo el guía."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:140
translate spanish hwb_s10b_a46a7b04:

    # Woman "They were just so darn clever. Really makes you wonder how they all ended up dying out, huh?"
    Woman "Они были просто чертовски смышлеными. И правда становится интересно, как они в конечном итоге вымерли, хах?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:142
translate spanish hwb_s10b_af82c5b5:

    # "Uhh…"
    "Ehh..."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:144
translate spanish hwb_s10b_18518bc7:

    # Amber "I’m pretty sure a lot of them are still alive. And like, some of them live here. In this canyon."
    Amber "Уверена, что многие из них все еще живы. И ну, некоторые живут здесь. В этом каньоне."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:146
translate spanish hwb_s10b_d407caa4:

    # "I had heard that much, at least. But apparently not everyone did."
    "Al menos eso lo había escuchado. Pero aparentemente no todos lo hicieron."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:148
translate spanish hwb_s10b_b1ebdcd3:

    # "For a second, the woman looks at me like I’m crazy. But then she busts up laughing."
    "Por un segundo, la mujer me mira como si estuviera loca. Pero luego se suelta a reír a carcajadas."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:152
translate spanish hwb_s10b_09ae76ee:

    # Woman "Sorry, sorry, you’re absolutely right! I was thinking of them Aztecs, down in Mexico!"
    Woman "Прости, прости, ты абсолютно права! Я думала, что он рассказывал про ацтеков в Центральной Мексике!"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:156
translate spanish hwb_s10b_76332f1e:

    # "Her laugh is more like a bray. She sounds like a farm animal. In my head, I keep hoping she’ll turn back around and leave us alone."
    "Su risa es más como un rebuzno. Suena como un animal de granja. En mi cabeza, sigo esperando que se dé la vuelta y nos deje en paz."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:158
translate spanish hwb_s10b_235e0573:

    # "But we’re not so lucky. She keeps on chatting us up as we follow the trail. I’m self-conscious about how noisy she’s being, compared to the low noise level of the other."
    "Pero no tenemos tanta suerte. Sigue conversando con nosotras mientras recorremos el sendero. Me siento cohibida por lo ruidosa que es, en comparación con el bajo nivel de ruido de los demás."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s10b_fa04be15:

    # Woman "Say, is that where the name ‘Texas’ comes from? From ‘Aztec?’"
    Woman "Скажи, откуда взялось название “Техас“? От “ацтек”?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s10b_74dcd3ae:

    # "Before I can answer, she’s started shouting at someone else."
    "Antes de que pueda responder, ya está gritándole a alguien más."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s10b_f89f6108:

    # Woman "Howard! Hey, Howard, come over here!"
    Woman "Говард! Эй, Говард, пади сюда!"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:174
translate spanish hwb_s10b_79d43df7:

    # "By now, nearly everyone is looking at us."
    "Para entonces, casi todos nos están mirando."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:176
translate spanish hwb_s10b_fec8c424:

    # Guide "M’am, can you please keep your voice down?"
    Guide "Мэм, не могли бы вы говорить потише?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s10b_25007076:

    # Woman "Oops, sorry!"
    Woman "Оой, извините!"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:180
translate spanish hwb_s10b_4228b7b8:

    # "She apologizes loudly."
    "Se disculpa a gritos."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s10b_237fcda5:

    # "So much for staying inconspicuous."
    "Adiós a pasar desapercibidas."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:184
translate spanish hwb_s10b_bbe0000a:

    # "Howard makes his way over. He looks rather defeated, face drooping and shoulders sagging. I figure he’s the woman’s husband."
    "Howard se acerca. Se ve bastante derrotado, con el rostro caído y los hombros hundidos. Supongo que es el esposo de la mujer."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6210ddbc:

    # Howard "Yes, dear?"
    Howard "Да, дорогая?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s10b_dbf6ede2:

    # Woman "I was just talking to this girl here, about history. And I was wonderin’, does the name ‘Texas’ have anything to do with the Aztecs? Since the words sound kinda similar?"
    Woman "Я тут разговаривала с этой девушкой, об истории. И мне стало интересно, связано ли как-то название “Техас” с ацтеками? Потому что слова вроде как звучат похоже."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s10b_be8ad044:

    # Howard "I don’t think so."
    Howard "Не думаю."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s10b_cd3f54ef:

    # Woman "Huh! Go figure!"
    Woman "Хм! Иди выясни!"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:224
translate spanish hwb_s10b_c3b0469f:

    # "She cackles again. Beside her, Howard sighs. For his sake, I hope her family is loaded or something."
    "Ella vuelve a reírse como una hiena. A su lado, Howard suspira. Por su bien, espero que su familia sea adinerada o algo así."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s10b_635a6693:

    # "Every time she laughs, the baby on her chest bounces. But the lucky kid sleeps right through it all. Maybe he’s used to this."
    "Cada vez que se ríe, el bebé en su pecho rebota. Pero el afortunado niño duerme durante todo el proceso. Quizás ya está acostumbrado."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:228
translate spanish hwb_s10b_5ae18946:

    # Woman "Anyway! I must have left my manners back in Wisconsin! My name’s Linda, and this’s my husband, Howard."
    Woman "Короче! Я наверное оставила свои манеры в Висконсине! Меня зовут Линда, а это мой муж Говард."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:230
translate spanish hwb_s10b_2836e333:

    # Linda "This little champ right here…"
    Linda "А этот маленький чемпион…"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s10b_b5cbbd2f:

    # "She thrusts herself and thus the baby towards me."
    "Se empuja a sí misma, y por ende al bebé, hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s10b_a289da4a:

    # Linda "Is Dino! Ain’t that just the cutest name?"
    Linda "Это Дино! Ну не милейшее ли имя."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s10b_807f3c05:

    # "I just grunt in response. I’m trying to see around her, up to where the guide is alternating between shooting Linda death glares and trying to narrate the walk."
    "Solo gruño en respuesta. Estoy tratando de ver a su alrededor, hacia donde el guía alterna entre lanzarle miradas asesinas a Linda e intentar narrar la caminata."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s10b_846e672f:

    # "If he’s said anything useful about the canyon in the past couple minutes, I’ve missed it entirely."
    "Si ha dicho algo útil sobre el cañón en los últimos minutos, me lo he perdido por completo."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s10b_0a8e1912:

    # "Glancing over at Marina, who has pulled away a couple feet, it looks like she’s enjoying my torture in struggling silence. Tears have formed at the corners of her eyes, glittering in the dying light."
    "Al mirar de reojo a Marina, que se ha alejado un par de pies, parece que está disfrutando de mi tortura en un silencio forzado. Se le han formado lágrimas en las comisuras de los ojos, brillando con la luz moribunda."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s10b_50e05abe:

    # "They’re the good kind of tears; the kind from laughing too much. Her hand is smooshed over her mouth and she’s shaking with the effort of staying silent."
    "Son lágrimas del tipo bueno; las que salen de reír demasiado. Tiene la mano aplastada sobre la boca y tiembla con el esfuerzo de permanecer en silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s10b_95fe17ac:

    # "There’s no way I can let her get away with that, especially since I need to get closer to the front for now."
    "No hay manera de que deje que se salga con la suya, especialmente porque necesito acercarme al frente por ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s10b_8a09e4b7:

    # "I grab her arm and tug her over into Linda’s line of sight."
    "Le agarro el brazo y la arrastro hasta el campo de visión de Linda."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s10b_f3093847:

    # Amber "I’m Jane."
    Amber "Меня зовут Джейн."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s10b_e340cbf3:

    # "The enthusiasm in my voice is so forced."
    "El entusiasmo en mi voz es tan forzado."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s10b_44dfd82b:

    # Jane "And this is my friend, Lacey."
    Jane "А это моя подруга, Лейси."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6182b464:

    # "I use fake names just to be safe."
    "Uso nombres falsos solo para estar segura."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s10b_f7803ec6:

    # "Marina limply shakes Linda’s hand, which has grabbed hers. The mirth has vanished from Marina's face."
    "Marina estrecha flojamente la mano de Linda, que le ha agarrado la suya. La alegría ha desaparecido del rostro de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s10b_c5fa6fdf:

    # "Good."
    "Bien."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s10b_bde1f205:

    # Lacey "Nice to meet you."
    Lacey "Приятно познакомиться."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s10b_c27a506a:

    # "Linda pumps her arm like a guillotine, grinning broadly and yet still managing to walk."
    "Linda bombea su brazo como una guillotina, sonriendo ampliamente y aun así logrando caminar."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s10b_ff9be924:

    # Linda "It’s so good to see young people takin’ an interest in nature and history and all that. Are y’all from around here? We’re originally from Tennessee, see, but moved to Wisconsin and…"
    Linda "Так прекрасно видеть молодое поколение, заинтересованное в природе и истории и во всем этом. А вы откуда? Мы вообще из Теннесси, понимаете, но переехали в Висконсин и…"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:291
translate spanish hwb_s10b_9ad8e5fe:

    # "Having been properly introduced, I leave Marina to suffer through the family history. I shift away and walk ahead, passing by most of the tour group, so that I can better hear the guide."
    "Una vez presentadas formalmente, dejo a Marina para que sufra la historia familiar. Me aparto y camino adelante, pasando a la mayor parte del grupo del tour, para poder escuchar mejor al guía."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s10b_0f598b19:

    # "For a while, he talks about the wildlife and history of the park. After a couple minutes though, the lessons become more relevant."
    "Por un rato, habla sobre la vida salvaje y la historia del parque. Sin embargo, después de un par de minutos, las lecciones se vuelven más relevantes."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s10b_25c97506:

    # Guide "We’ll be coming up on the Mummy Cave Ruins here in just a little bit. That’s one of the better known sites in the Canyon. Seven hundred years ago, it was a bustling Puebloan village."
    Guide "Мы подойдем к руинам «Пещеры Мумий» совсем скоро. Это одно из самых известных достопримечательностей в Каньоне. Семьсот лет назад здесь была оживленная деревня племени Пуэбло."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s10b_0e44db9a:

    # Guide "We can’t get too close to the ruins, so unfortunately it might be a little too late to really see them clearly tonight."
    Guide "Мы не можем подойти к руинам слишком близко, поэтому, к сожалению, сейчас может быть, уже довольно поздно, чтобы хорошенько разглядеть их в такой темноте."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6f4ceffa:

    # Guide "While the Mummy Cave itself hasn’t ever been open to the public…"
    Guide "Так как «Пещера Мумий» никогда не была открыта для широкой публики…"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:314
translate spanish hwb_s10b_9a68ca1f:

    # "That’s all I needed to know, so I start to slip back towards Marina is still a conversational hostage."
    "Eso es todo lo que necesitaba saber, así que empiezo a regresar hacia Marina, que sigue siendo una rehén conversacional."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6ec73652:

    # "Linda notices me approaching."
    "Linda nota que me acerco."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s10b_469738dd:

    # Linda "Oh, Jane, there you are. I was just telling Lacey about one of the cows I helped birth when I was younger!"
    Linda "О, Джейн, вот ты где. Я как раз рассказывала Лейси про одну из коров, которой я помогла родить, когда была еще молода!"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s10b_b14cde05:

    # "I’m not sure how the conversation went from introductions to cow birth in such a short span of time, but I’m not curious enough to ask."
    "No estoy segura de cómo la conversación pasó de presentaciones a nacimiento de vacas en tan poco tiempo, pero no tengo suficiente curiosidad para preguntar."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s10b_dffb72b4:

    # "When I rejoin Marina, she mouths two words."
    "Cuando me reúno con Marina, articula dos palabras con los labios."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:336
translate spanish hwb_s10b_9dc10f54:

    # Marina "Save. {w=1.0}Me."
    Marina "Спаси. {w=1.0}Меня."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s10b_d97497b1:

    # "I don’t know how to get out of this one. Annoyance aside, it’ll be impossible to slip away with Linda’s attention on us."
    "No sé cómo salir de esta. Aparte del fastidio, será imposible escabullirnos con la atención de Linda sobre nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:340
translate spanish hwb_s10b_d3b25142:

    # "But it seems we’re in luck. As we go around another bend in the road, something more interesting than Marina and me comes into view."
    "Pero parece que tenemos suerte. Al dar la vuelta en otra curva del camino, algo más interesante que Marina y yo aparece a la vista."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s10b_8d9c8e4b:

    # Linda "Oh, Howard, look! This is it! This is those Mummy Ruins I was telling you about."
    Linda "О, Говард, посмотри! Вот оно! Вот те самые руины «Пещеры Мумий», о которых я тебе рассказывала."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s10b_c96766e3:

    # "Linda elbows forward, moving ahead of us."
    "Linda se abre paso con los codos, moviéndose delante de nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s10b_1e188e67:

    # Linda "You girls make sure you get a good spot, you’re gonna wanna see this, even if it’s dark out."
    Linda "Вы, девочки, поторопитесь и займите хорошее местечко, если хотите это увидеть, хотя уже довольно темно."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:354
translate spanish hwb_s10b_16666d56:

    # "She forges ahead, her husband trailing dutifully. As he passes, I think I hear him say ‘sorry,’ though I’m not certain."
    "Ella avanza con determinación, su esposo siguiéndola obedientemente. Al pasar, creo oírle decir 'lo siento', aunque no estoy segura."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:361
translate spanish hwb_s10b_7f49962a:

    # "Once they’re out of earshot, Marina makes a sound like a train letting out steam."
    "Una vez que están fuera del alcance del oído, Marina hace un sonido como un tren soltando vapor."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:363
translate spanish hwb_s10b_04eb50bc:

    # Marina "Oh. {w=0.4} My. {w=0.4} God. {w=0.4} I thought I was gonna explode. My ears or my head or my brain or something!"
    Marina "О. {w=0.4} Мой. {w=0.4} Бог. {w=0.4} Я думала, что взорвусь. Либо мои уши, либо голова, либо мозг!"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:367
translate spanish hwb_s10b_5a938279:

    # Amber "Saw you laughing and figured it wasn’t fair if I was the only one who suffered."
    Amber "Я видела, как ты смеешься, и подумала, что будет несправедливо, если единственной мученицей буду я."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:371
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6bb8a9f3:

    # Marina "Ugh, I’d take it all back if I could."
    Marina "Ох, если бы я только могла вернуть время, я бы не смеялась тогда."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:375
translate spanish hwb_s10b_3b826c91:

    # Marina "Seriously though, first she was talking about herself, then about her kid, then about her childhood, and then she started talking about growing up on a farm."
    Marina "Нет, серьезно, сначала она рассказывала о себе, потом про своего ребенка, потом о своем детстве, а потом про то, как росла на ферме."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s10b_1e93040f:

    # Marina "Somehow she ended up going on about cows having babies and how messy it all is? I don’t even know."
    Marina "Как произошло, что она уже начала рассказывать про коровьи роды и про то, как это было мерзко? Я вообще не знаю."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:379
translate spanish hwb_s10b_4dc8c7bf:

    # Amber "What, you’re not interested in that stuff?"
    Amber "Что, неужели тебе это неинтересно?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s10b_51b2d570:

    # Marina "Ew, no! Gross, gross, gross!"
    Marina "Фу, нет! Мерзость, мерзость, мерзость!"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:385
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6d63e241:

    # "She wrinkles up her face as she says it."
    "Arruga la cara mientras lo dice."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:389
translate spanish hwb_s10b_a1959e61:

    # "I giggle, but then turn serious real fast."
    "Me río, pero luego me pongo seria muy rápido."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:393
translate spanish hwb_s10b_450b1f56:

    # Amber "Okay, but listen."
    Amber "Ладно, но слушай."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s10b_338bc8d8:

    # Amber "Because it’s dark, the group probably isn’t gonna stop to look at the Mummy Cave Ruins for very long. So we’ll have to wait until we can sneak away again, and then go over there ourselves."
    Amber "Из-за того, что сейчас темно, группа не собирается останавливаться надолго, чтобы посмотреть на руины «Пещеры Мумий». Поэтому нужно подождать, пока мы сможем улизнуть, и потом сами тут все осмотрим."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s10b_4835e153:

    # Marina "How far away are they?"
    Marina "Они далеко отсюда?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:403
translate spanish hwb_s10b_60b82a3f:

    # Amber "No idea. I can’t see from here. Just follow my lead again."
    Amber "Понятия не имею. Отсюда не видно. Просто иди за мной."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:411
translate spanish hwb_s10b_2ede2024:

    # Marina "Got it."
    Marina "Окей."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:415
translate spanish hwb_s10b_dc9457ef:

    # "We’ve been at the very back of the group the entire time. The people right in front of us are much less interested in us than Linda was, so I don’t think anyone will notice if we go missing."
    "Hemos estado al final del grupo todo el tiempo. La gente justo delante de nosotras está mucho menos interesada en nosotras de lo que lo estaba Linda, así que no creo que nadie note si desaparecemos."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:417
translate spanish hwb_s10b_cca3622e:

    # "When we reach a railing, the guide stops to point out the ruins. They’re across a small valley, a couple hundred yards away. In the darkness, it’s almost impossible to see them."
    "Cuando llegamos a una barandilla, el guía se detiene para señalar las ruinas. Están al otro lado de un pequeño valle, a un par de cientos de yardas. En la oscuridad, es casi imposible verlas."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:419
translate spanish hwb_s10b_03e901e8:

    # "They’re just a dark smudge against the even darker backdrop of a mountain."
    "Solo son una mancha oscura contra el fondo aún más oscuro de una montaña."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:421
translate spanish hwb_s10b_775e00d0:

    # "Marina and I are a few yards away from the group, too."
    "Marina y yo también estamos a unos metros del grupo."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:423
translate spanish hwb_s10b_a7946cc1:

    # "I pretend to inspect something on a rock, though there’s nothing there."
    "Finjo inspeccionar algo en una roca, aunque no hay nada allí."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s10b_828555c4:

    # "As the short speech ends and the guide starts to lead everyone on again, I dart behind a rock and crouch down. Marina quickly follows."
    "Cuando el breve discurso termina y el guía comienza a llevar a todos de nuevo, me escabullo detrás de una roca y me agacho. Marina me sigue rápidamente."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s10b_94eddd64:

    # "I can see her start to say something, but I cup my hand over her mouth before she can get a word out. Silently, I shake my head."
    "La veo empezar a decir algo, pero le cubro la boca con la mano antes de que pueda pronunciar una palabra. En silencio, niego con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s10b_9c814b63:

    # "Marina nods twice, so I uncover her face."
    "Marina asiente dos veces, así que le descubro el rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s10b_81b170ce:

    # "In my head, I count to 60. Once a minute has passed, I peel myself away from the rock and stand back up."
    "En mi cabeza, cuento hasta 60. Cuando ha pasado un minuto, me separo de la roca y me pongo de pie."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s10b_244705fd:

    # Amber "We should be safe now."
    Amber "Сейчас мы должны быть в безопасности."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s10b_d3dce968:

    # "Marina’s face lights up and she claps her hands. I notice that she’s taken out the journal page with the hiding spot again."
    "El rostro de Marina se ilumina y aplaude. Noto que ha sacado de nuevo la página del diario con el escondite."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:460
translate spanish hwb_s10b_3d6740ff:

    # Marina "That was so cool! It was like something out of a video game, where you just sneak away right in front of everyone!"
    Marina "Было так круто! Будто момент из видео игры, где ты пытаешься улизнуть прямо из-под носа у всех!"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:464
translate spanish hwb_s10b_f4df2c94:

    # Amber "Marina, we're going to need to have a very existential talk when we get back to the RV."
    Amber "Марина, когда вернемся в трейлер, нам нужно будет с тобой серьезно поговорить."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6a6b1ea3:

    # Amber "I guess so. But we still can’t be noisy. They’re not gonna be that far away."
    Amber "Думаю да. Но на все еще нельзя шуметь. Они не могли уйти слишком далеко."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:470
translate spanish hwb_s10b_839a6ff2:

    # Amber "No flashlights either."
    Amber "И без фонарей."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:474
translate spanish hwb_s10b_a827f016:

    # "This close up, I can see her face fall at that."
    "Tan de cerca, puedo ver cómo se le cae la cara al oír eso."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s10b_3565fa31:

    # Amber "Don’t worry, I’ll be right beside you."
    Amber "Не беспокойся, я буду рядом."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:482
translate spanish hwb_s10b_5557e196:

    # Marina "Are we just going to hop the fence and walk over there?"
    Marina "Мы просто перепрыгнем через ограду и пойдем прямо туда?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:486
translate spanish hwb_s10b_b016f88b:

    # Amber "Unless you have any better ideas."
    Amber "Если только у тебя нет плана получше."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:488
translate spanish hwb_s10b_3b3daa66:

    # Marina "What if they catch us?"
    Marina "А что если они нас поймают?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:492
translate spanish hwb_s10b_1dc1f738:

    # Amber "Then they’ll throw us out."
    Amber "Тогда они нас вышвырнут."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:496
translate spanish hwb_s10b_d04a116d:

    # Marina "We’re not gonna get arrested for trespassing or anything, are we?"
    Marina "Нас же не арестуют за нарушение границ или типа того, ведь так?"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:498
translate spanish hwb_s10b_694dce4a:

    # Amber "Nah, that’d be too much trouble for them."
    Amber "Неа, это бы доставило им слишком много хлопот."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:500
translate spanish hwb_s10b_840b8059:

    # "I say that, although I don’t actually know."
    "Digo eso, aunque en realidad no lo sé."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:504
translate spanish hwb_s10b_5d000463:

    # Marina "Okay…"
    Marina "Ладно…"

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:506
translate spanish hwb_s10b_1ad673e1:

    # "The uncertainty in her voice is obvious."
    "La incertidumbre en su voz es obvia."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:511
translate spanish hwb_s10b_6d52593c:

    # "I grab the paper from her hands and stuff it into my pocket."
    "Le arrebato el papel de las manos y lo meto en mi bolsillo."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s10b_999ef651:

    # Amber "Let’s go. The longer we wait, the more likely it is that they'll notice us missing."
    Amber "Пойдем. Чем дольше мы ждем, тем вероятнее, что они заметят наше исчезновение."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s10b_3eb30d07:

    # "I stroll over to the metal rail, hoping that I sound more confident than I am. Honestly, this is pretty risky, and more than a little stupid."
    "Camino tranquilamente hacia la barandilla de metal, esperando sonar más segura de lo que estoy. Honestamente, esto es bastante arriesgado y más que un poco estúpido."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:521
translate spanish hwb_s10b_b4b0637a:

    # "But it’s also exciting."
    "Pero también es emocionante."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:526
translate spanish hwb_s10b_d08bf9e5:

    # "I duck down and underneath the rail. After a moment, Marina does the same."
    "Me agacho y paso por debajo de la barandilla. Después de un momento, Marina hace lo mismo."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:528
translate spanish hwb_s10b_2ab88175:

    # "We’re officially out of bounds."
    "Estamos oficialmente fuera de los límites."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:530
translate spanish hwb_s10b_4eca254f:

    # "Across the small field, I can still just barely make out the shape of the ruins. They sit close to the mouth of a large cave that runs up the mountain like a scar."
    "Al otro lado del pequeño campo, todavía puedo distinguir apenas la silueta de las ruinas. Están cerca de la entrada de una gran cueva que sube por la montaña como una cicatriz."

# game/script/hwb_s10b.rpy:532
translate spanish hwb_s10b_a64e051e:

    # Amber "Okay, come on."
    Amber "Ладно, пойдем."

